review_text: Outstanding experience! The Masala Chai  Chole Bhature  Gulab Jamun (2 pcs)  and Vegetable Biryani exceeded all expectations. Chole Bhature was the star of the meal. Will definitely order again!
Absolutely amazing Gajar Halwa  Gulab Jamun (2 pcs)  and Naan! The Gulab Jamun (2 pcs) was cooked to perfection. Fresh ingredients and authentic flavors. Highly recommend!
Best Indian food in UAE! Lamb Rogan Josh  Garlic Naan  and Aloo Tikki Chaat were incredible. Garlic Naan had the perfect balance of spices. Five stars!
Great food overall. Garlic Naan and Masala Chai were tasty  especially the Masala Chai. Would order again!
Good quality food. Dal Makhani  Masala Chai  Tandoori Roti  and Chicken Tikka Masala were nicely done. Masala Chai could have been slightly spicier but still good!
